  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nAdd support for modifying storage arrays\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nA possible function call could be:\r\n`await myContract.smodify.array.push('myArray', 123);` in order to push 123\r\n`await myContract.smodify.array.set('myArray', 0, 123);` in order to set 123 to the index 0\r\n`await myContract.smodify.array.remove('myArray', 0);` in order to delete the item at the index 0",
